org.gridlab.gridsphere.services.security.gss
Interface HttpgServiceResource

All Superinterfaces:
GssConnectionResource, GssEnabledResource, Resource, ServiceResource, WebServiceResource
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseHttpgServiceResource
public interface HttpgServiceResource
extends WebServiceResource, GssConnectionResource

Describes a httpg service resource. The httpg protocol is not formally supported by Globus anymore, but it is still used in some projects, notably the GridLab Project.
